==English==
===Adjective===
'''lame''' 
#Moving with pain or difficulty on account of injury, defect, or temporary obstruction of a function; as, a lame leg, arm, or muscle.
#To some degree disabled by reason of the imperfect action of a limb; crippled; as, a lame man.
#Hence, hobbling; limping; inefficient; imperfect.
#See Amin Bahubeshi


== Amin Bahubeshi ==

An amin is a muslim boy, who is not very desirable in the looks but has a very intellectual mind and has a very good personality. He is also a good confidant. He is also quite lame.

